<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Tax Call Invitation</title>
  </head>
  <body
    style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; padding: 20px;"
  >
    <table
      style="max-width:600px; width:100%; margin:auto; border-collapse: collapse;"
    >
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">
          <h2 style="color: #2a7ae2;">Hi {{name}},</h2>
          <p>Congratulations on taking the first step—now let’s take some time
            to start clearing the path forward.</p>
          <p>On this call, we’ll contact the taxing authority together. We’ll
            gather information on balances, missing returns, flags, and anything
            else affecting your case. This isn’t guesswork—it's a fact-finding
            mission that saves you hours of hold time and confusion.</p>
          <p>This call lays the foundation for everything we’ll do from here.
            It’s simple, it’s fast, and don’t worry—we will do all the talking.</p>
          <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-weight: bold;">Let's get started
            today!</p>
          <p>Call me directly at
            <a
              href="tel:{{phone}}"
              style="color: #2a7ae2; text-decoration: none;"
            >{{phone}}</a>
          </p>

          <div style="margin-top: 40px;">
            {{{signature}}}
          </div>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>